thread.title: Deepa Gopal
thread.title_full: Ink Station reviewed by Deepa Gopal

author: Deepa Gopal
title: Deepa Gopal
text: I needed to print a few documents urgently, & realized my printer had run out of ink. This was somewhere after lunch, & Google Search recommended to purchase through Ink Station. I got the ink next working day at my doorstep as early as 8am. That's excellent service. Thanks Ink Station!
